Oh, there's no need.

20:39.371 --> 20:44.866
There's probably a whole army
of paramedics waiting for me out front.

20:45.044 --> 20:46.534
Well...

20:46.712 --> 20:50.080
...you take care of yourself out there,
young man.

20:50.883 --> 20:52.373
I will, sir.

20:57.990 --> 20:59.981
[LAUGHS]

21:00.893 --> 21:02.361
Damn it.

21:02.528 --> 21:07.227
Sometimes I did keep...

21:07.399 --> 21:10.892
...inside the lines.

21:23.315 --> 21:25.249
