21:25.417 --> 21:28.614
The Radio City Rockettes are here.

21:31.090 --> 21:32.148
Send them home, Mac.

21:32.324 --> 21:34.019
Oh, thank you, sir.

21:34.193 --> 21:38.426
I didn't know whether to bring them in
one at a time or all in a row kicking.

21:38.931 --> 21:41.093
I'm sure you would have made
the right decision.

21:41.267 --> 21:43.292
Uh-huh.

